  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 12",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Tyrion II</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n132 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_4\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 4\">Tyrion I</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 11\">Jaime II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tyrion II</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_13\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 13\">Arya II</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 19\">Tyrion III</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> is waiting in <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>' room when the eunuch walks in. The Spider reveals that <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> means to restore <a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a>, since the archmaesters of the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> claim that “only the conclave can unmake a Grand Maester”. When the conclave meant to send Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gormon_Tyrell\" title=\"Gormon Tyrell\">Gormon</a>, Lord Tywin acted at once, not wishing another <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">Tyrell</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Small_Council\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Small Council\">Small Council</a>. \n</p><p>Tyrion is surprised to learn that Varys has whisperers even in the Citadel, where the conclave always meets in secrecy. He finds out that <a href=\"/index.php/Boros_Blount\" title=\"Boros Blount\">Boros Blount</a> has been restored to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>, and that <a href=\"/index.php/Mandon_Moore\" title=\"Mandon Moore\">Mandon Moore</a> had been brought to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a>. Tyrion asks Varys to bring <a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">Shae</a> to the eunuch's chambers so that no one will notice their meeting. He realizes that he cannot trust Varys any further, but hopes to use him this one last time. When he meets Shae, he means to send her away to protect her from his father, but Tyrion once again cannot bear to part with her. He also knows he must deal with the singer <a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Silver_Tongue\" title=\"Symon Silver Tongue\">Symon Silver Tongue</a> if he means to keep Shae in King's Landing.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pycelle\" title=\"Pycelle\">Pycelle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gormon_Tyrell\" title=\"Gormon Tyrell\">Gormon Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Boros_Blount\" title=\"Boros Blount\">Boros Blount</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mandon_Moore\" title=\"Mandon Moore\">Mandon Moore</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">Shae</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Silver_Tongue\" title=\"Symon Silver Tongue\">Symon Silver Tongue</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Small_Council\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Small Council\">Small Council</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_12&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from AOL member vbkorik27 previously at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a>.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2012/11/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-7\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 7</a>; summary and analyses of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.nl/2012/11/re-read-tyrion-ii-caught-in-riddle.html\">Re-read: Tyrion II caught in riddle</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynth.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403152518\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.045 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.183 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1096/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7884/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1237/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40